<Link id="l00823" /><CodeLine lineNumber="823"><Highlight kind="normal">    ScopeKind Kind = ScopeKind::Attribute;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00824" /><CodeLine lineNumber="824"><Highlight kind="normal">    </Highlight><Highlight kind="keywordflow">if</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"> (ScopeHistory.empty() || ScopeHistory.back().Context != Scope::Object) &#123;</Highlight></CodeLine>
